Ganache is a Private Simulated Blockchain Network with a wallet having 10 accounts holding 100 eth each. 
The following steps can be followed to setup and explore ganache and truffle framework

1. Download ganache from https://www.trufflesuite.com/ganache and install
2. Download and install node.js 
3. use "npm install -g truffle" to setup truffle framework
4. "truffle unbox <project> can be used to download an existing project from truffle
5. "truffle compile" sets up the downloaded project
5. "truffle migrate" is used for deploying

Truffle commands are
truffle init
truffle develop
truffle console
truffle debug
truffle test
truffle publish
